ch the client's fiscal period ends. Only one engagement per client per tax year is permitted. A new engagement is created at status START.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Successful engaâ€¦","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Create a client engagement\\nThe system SHALL allow an authenticatâ€¦","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:00:33.586Z","title":"Write","type":"file_write"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mqvrw8jv_00af123f953d":{"observation":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrw8jv_00af123f953d","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Admin workflow dashboard page\\nThe system SHALL provide a `/admin/workflow` page accessible only to authenticated admins. The page SHALL display a table of all client engagements across all tax years. Table columns: Client Name, Business Type, Tax Year, Status, Last Updated, Last Updated By. The table SHALL support filtering by Status and by Bâ€¦","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Admin workflow dashboard page\\nThe system SHALL provide a `/adminâ€¦","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:00:55.976Z","title":"Write","type":"file_write"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mqvrwdfi_6a93e8f029b1":{"observation":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqvrwdfi_6a93e8f029b1","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"command\":\"openspec status --change client-workflow --json 2>&1\",\"description\":\"Check artifact status after writing specs\"} | {\"interrupted\":false,\"isImage\":false,\"noOutputExpected\":false,\"stderr\":\"\",\"stdout\":\"{\\n  \\\"changeName\\\": \\\"client-workflow\\\",\\n  \\\"schemaName\\\": \\\"superpowers-driven\\\",\\n  \\\"isComplete\\\": false,\\n  \\\"applyRequires\\\": [\\n    \\\"tasks\\